<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234668>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 10. Sycorax konopiki Ježek sp. nov. male. 1. Head, frontal view. 2. Facets in detail, frontal view. 3. Basal antennomeres, some ascoids omitted. 4. Maxilla and palpus maxillaris. 5. Pharynx, cibarium and mandibles, dorsal view. 6. Wing. 7. Epandrium and cerci, dorsal view. 8. Gonocoxite and gonostyle, dorsal view. 9. Aedeagal complex, dorsal view. 10. Same, lateral view. [Scale: 6 = 0.5 mm; 1 – 5, 7, 9 – 10 = 0.1 mm; 8 = 0.01 mm]" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234668/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234671>
    dc:description "FIGURE 37. Specimens of Sycorax konopiki sp. nov. (males) resting on the frog Ansonia leptopus (Photo: O. Konopik)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234671/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

